    <item>
      <title>富士康表示，在本田合并谈判期间，其对日产的兴趣暂时搁置</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/foxconn-interest-in-nissan-said-on-hold-amid-honda-merger-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，总部位于台湾的 iPhone 制造商富士康，由于日产汽车正与本田汽车就合并事宜进行谈判，因此该公司暂时搁置了收购日产汽车的意向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/foxconn-interest-in-nissan-said-on-hold-amid-honda-merger-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 09:36:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称俄罗斯重大网络攻击袭击国家登记处</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ukraine-says-major-russian-cyberattack-hits-state-registries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰内阁在 Telegram 上表示，周四俄罗斯黑客发起的大规模攻击导致乌克兰司法部管理的国家登记系统暂时停止运行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ukraine-says-major-russian-cyberattack-hits-state-registries</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 08:57:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国首席执行官选择人工智能、住房和太空矿山作为 2025 年的最大主题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/uk-ceos-pick-ai-housing-and-space-mines-as-some-of-2025-s-biggest-themes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年可谓忙碌的一年：唐纳德·特朗普再次当选，利率下调，地缘政治紧张局势加剧。新年将至，彭博新闻采访了十几位英国首席执行官，探讨 2025 年的展望。以下是来自金融、建筑和能源等多个行业的老板的见解，以及英国上市公司的关键主题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/uk-ceos-pick-ai-housing-and-space-mines-as-some-of-2025-s-biggest-themes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>腾讯与荣耀在人工智能和云领域建立广泛合作伙伴关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/tencent-and-honor-forge-wide-ranging-partnership-on-ai-and-cloud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据周五的一份声明称，腾讯控股有限公司与荣耀终端有限公司将在云计算和人工智能开发方面开展长期战略合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/tencent-and-honor-forge-wide-ranging-partnership-on-ai-and-cloud</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 06:44:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SAP 提拔一名经理，免遭多次骚扰指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/sap-promoted-manager-after-repeated-accusations-of-harassment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曾在该科技巨头 Signavio 部门的团队领导手下工作的女性表示，该公司未能解决有关欺凌和歧视的投诉。SAP 表示，它对虐待行为采取零容忍政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/sap-promoted-manager-after-repeated-accusations-of-harassment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 05:00:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>取消 Tether 可能让欧洲错过特朗普加密货币热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/tether-mica-exit-puts-europe-at-risk-of-missing-crypto-boom-usdt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟加密资产监管法规将于年底全面生效，此举将重塑一种关键数字代币的市场，在加密货币皈依者唐纳德·特朗普准备在美国就职之际，有可能削弱欧盟对投资者的吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/tether-mica-exit-puts-europe-at-risk-of-missing-crypto-boom-usdt</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微信送礼工具助推腾讯及相关股票上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/tencent-related-stocks-jump-as-wechat-gifting-tool-fuels-buying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受投资者对其热门微信平台新赠送功能的热情推动，腾讯控股有限公司及其相关股票周五上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/tencent-related-stocks-jump-as-wechat-gifting-tool-fuels-buying</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 03:13:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>颠覆性的 10 分钟送达服务进军印度食品行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/disruptive-10-minute-deliveries-spread-to-india-s-food-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着数字平台之间争夺不耐烦消费者的竞争愈演愈烈，印度的外卖配送应用承诺在 10 分钟内将印度香饭和热饮送到顾客家门口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/disruptive-10-minute-deliveries-spread-to-india-s-food-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度首次公开募股 (IPO) 规模达 190 亿美元，创历史新高，今年将是印度又一个辉煌的一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/banner-year-beckons-again-for-india-after-19-billion-ipo-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度已成为全球领先的首次公开募股 (IPO) 等交易市场之一，随着投资者抢占市场机会，印度今年的融资额创下了纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/banner-year-beckons-again-for-india-after-19-billion-ipo-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 01:26:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索尼创纪录的股价上涨让投资者对游戏行业更加看好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/sony-s-record-climb-makes-investors-more-bullish-on-gaming-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索尼集团公司 (Sony Group Corp.) 期待已久的股价创下历史新高，鼓舞了看涨的投资者和分析师，他们预计，由于视频游戏前景强劲，其涨势将延续到 2025 年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/sony-s-record-climb-makes-investors-more-bullish-on-gaming-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
